underlying_goal: To commit a set of staged changes by logically grouping them.
primary_success: Correctly analyzing a set of changes and splitting them into five logical commits covering documentation, classifier improvements, bug fixes, caching, and cleanup.
brief_summary: The user requested to commit staged changes. Claude analyzed the diff, identified five logically distinct groups of changes (documentation, classifier improvements, bug fixes, caching, and cleanup), and created a separate, well-messaged commit for each group.
